    <div class="body">
        <p>It seems that wikification does not support documentation inline links.</p>

<p> links are not displayed but completly suppressed.
 links are only displayed as text but not as link.</p>

<p>See Zend_Date chapter Overview 
             
does not display in wikification</p>

<pre><code>        &lt;link linkend="zend.locale.date.normalize"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Zend_Locale_Format::getDate()&lt;/code&gt;
        &lt;/link&gt;
</code></pre>

<p>is only displayed as text but not as link.
It seems that "linkend" as in-document-link is not supported.</p>

<p>This should be integrated if possible. It's not only used in Zend_Date but also in other documentation parts.</p>

